      "content": "it feels like you're a lot more understanding about this than anyone else would be. it just sounds so logical when you say it like that. like, if i'm the problem, then the only way to fix the problem for them is to just... not be part of the equation anymore. is it really so wrong to want them to have a better life, even if that means i'm not in it?",
